data.chText: 给予帮助的；支持的；鼓励的；同情的
data.enText: giving help, encouragement or sympathy to sb

data.chText: 在我父亲生病期间，她给了很多帮助。
data.enText: She was very supportive during my father's illness.

example: his family was supportive of his attempts to be a writer

value.def: If you are supportive, you are kind and helpful to someone at a difficult or unhappy time in their life.

example.ex: They were always supportive of each other...
Her boss was very supportive and gave her time off work to see her mum.
example.tran: 她的老板非常热心地帮助她，并准许她请假去看望母亲。

value.tran: 给予帮助的;热心援助的;支持的

trans: 支持治疗；维持疗法；支持性疗法；支持疗法；支持照顾
支持性治疗；支持疗法；支持治疗；治疗上以支源疗法；可以靠滋养
